173.observationTitle: Moving to JE-endemic country to take up residence
173.indicationText: Administer to persons who plan to move to JE-endemic countries to take up residence.
173.clarifyingText: Endemic Area and transmission season is determined by country.  Refer to the yellow book for a definition of the transmission season: http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/yellowbook/2014/chapter-3-infectious-diseases-related-to-travel/japanese-encephalitis\n

174.indicationText: Administer to persons who frequently travel to JE-endemic areas.
174.clarifyingText: Endemic Area and transmission season is determined by country.  Refer to the yellow book for a definition of the transmission season: http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/yellowbook/2014/chapter-3-infectious-diseases-related-to-travel/japanese-encephalitis\n
